data.description: Price reduced for quick sale.  "AS IS" This 3 bedroom/2 ½ bath home is between Inverness and Crystal River,  you can swim with manatees and fish for fresh and saltwater dinners.  It is less than an hour to the Tampa airport and 5 minutes to all the shopping you could possibly want. The home is on a 1/3-acre corner lot, one block off Hwy 44, but on a dead-end street. Besides the garage, in the backyard, you have an additional shed.  Outside the screen room is your own 6-person hot tub. The yard is completely fenced. This is an open floor plan with an eat-in bar.
